---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

import { SITE_TITLE } from '../consts';
---

<BaseLayout title={`About - ${SITE_TITLE}`} description="My curriculum vitae">
  <div class="space-y-12">
    <section>
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">추 나린</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">Software Engineer, CS Student</p>
      <div class="flex gap-4 mt-4 text-sm">
        <a href="mailto:choonarine@gmail.com">Email</a>
        <a href="https://github.com/choonarine">GitHub</a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/yourprofile">LinkedIn</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 border-b border-zinc-200 pb-2 dark:border-zinc-800">Experience</h2>
      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">축제 투표 시스템 Backend Development</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">광양고등학교 • 2018 - 2020</p>
          <ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
            <li>Flask → FastAPI 백엔드 개발, SQLite 사용</li>
            <li>PM2, nginx를 이용한 CI/CD 파이프라인 구현</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 border-b border-zinc-200 pb-2 dark:border-zinc-800">Education</h2>
      <div class="space-y-4">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Kyonggi University</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">2026 - Present</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold">Code : Zero 코딩 동아리</h3>
          <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400">광양고등학교 • 2023 - 2025</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 border-b border-zinc-200 pb-2 dark:border-zinc-800">Skills</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
        {['React', 'JS/TS', 'Python', 'FastAPI', 'SQL', 'Git', 'Docker', 'C/C++', 'Linux', 'Git'].map((skill) => (
          <span class="border border-zinc-300 px-2 py-1 text-sm dark:border-zinc-700">
            {skill}
          </span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 border-b border-zinc-200 pb-2 dark:border-zinc-800">Projects</h2>
      <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-zinc-700 dark:text-zinc-300">
        <li><a class="font-bold" href="/projects">프로젝트 확인</a></li>
      </ul>
    </section>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
